Congratulations to all of the incredible athletes involved in the 2016 Rio Olympics!
Each and every athlete we watched take the field at the Rio Olympics needed two things to get there: calcium and protein, two things that kids and adults don’t get enough of. Milk, it’s that rich taste kids love and the nutrition they need.
Milk is more than just a rich, nutritious beverage that creates great memories for our kids. All those world-class athletes at the 2016 Rio Olympics? Without the bone-protecting calcium and muscle-growing proteins contained in milk, those athletic dreams may never have become a reality. Milk, it’s that rich taste kids love and the nutrition they need.
